title: Creating Ranked Team- 5 Wins (15 points) For the Ranked rewards!
body:
Hey all! I'll keep it simple.
 
* Creating a ranked 5s team with the aim to get the rewards before end of season (November 7th)  _It's five wins at minimum, so frequency over the next month won't be as regular as once a day, however if you are frequent then great, we may just aim for more :)_

* Would _prefer_ to have Gold+ Players participate, but I'll be happy to take in silvers, just be sure to respectfully listen to a person's tips  or calls during the game, and use it to improve!

Anyone interested leave a comment down below with your **Rank, Role(s) & IGN**, and i'll be sure to follow it up! 
**GL HF**
